{
  "stem": "18470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that's how I learned-- I learned English through my-- through the ear, largely by attending lots and lots of movies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They also filled my fantasy life as a kid, see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Immediately almost, in the fall of '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to PS 172.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had wonderful teachers there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, as far as I can remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had the tradition of English teachers, British teachers, in the public schools.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they taught me great respect for the English sentence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the little I know of the English language they taught me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, language is the key.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father learned English, because he learned-- he was a quick study.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a very fine mathematician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he probably, if he had his druthers, that's what he would have wanted to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother never really mastered it, and she had neologisms that were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One day we're walking down Fifth Avenue, and she sees a very attractive man all spatted up and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she says to me, Alfred, look at that man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Doesn't he look extinguished?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she would come up with these malapropisms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she had a great eye, and she could spell-- smell a phony across the room faster than anybody I've ever met.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were intuitive gifts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents were very different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One was very rational.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other was very emotional.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What is unusual is that we brought these hundreds of family photographs with us, postcards, and settings of the family in Oberwesel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would go through these regularly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'd say this is aunt so-and-so, uncle so-and-so, and to this day, these people have been dead many, many years.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
